---
import Landing from '../layouts/Landing.astro';
---

<Landing
	title="Examples — mcp-flowgate"
	description="Worked examples showing mcp-flowgate in action: content publishing, expense approval, TDD enforcement, deploy pipelines, and more."
>

<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 backdrop-blur-md bg-slate-950/80 border-b border-slate-800">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
		<a href="/" class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">mcp-flowgate</a>
		<div class="flex items-center gap-8">
			<a href="/introduction" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors">Docs</a>
			<a href="/examples" class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Examples</a>
			<a href="/blog" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors">Blog</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors">GitHub</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</nav>

<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 bg-white min-h-screen">
	<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Examples</h1>
		<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl">
			Each example is a complete, runnable config you can clone and modify.
			They're ordered from simple to complex — start at the top if
			you're new.
		</p>

		<div class="grid gap-8">

			<!-- Content Publish -->
			<div class="example-card">
				<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Content publishing</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
							<code>examples/content-publish/</code>
						</p>
					</div>
					<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/tree/main/examples/content-publish"
						class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap">
						View source
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
					A governed content pipeline: draft → brand review → human approval → publish.
					The LLM walks the workflow through links. When it reaches the approval
					gate, governance stops it cold — only a human can approve.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">governance</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">human approval</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">HATEOAS</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">actor enforcement</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Expense Approval -->
			<div class="example-card">
				<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Expense approval</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
							<code>examples/expense-approval/</code>
						</p>
					</div>
					<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/tree/main/examples/expense-approval"
						class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap">
						View source
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
					Multi-tenant expense workflow with two-tier approval. Small expenses
					need one manager. Large expenses need quorum evidence from multiple
					approvers. Payment is idempotent — the executor won't double-pay.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">multi-tenant</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">quorum</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">evidence guards</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">expr guards</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Deploy Pipeline -->
			<div class="example-card">
				<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Deploy pipeline</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
							<code>examples/deploy-pipeline/</code>
						</p>
					</div>
					<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/tree/main/examples/deploy-pipeline"
						class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap">
						View source
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
					Deterministic chaining in action. Lint → test → build auto-execute
					without LLM involvement. The model calls <code>workflow.start</code>
					once and gets the result at the deploy decision — three executor calls,
					zero LLM round trips.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">deterministic chaining</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">phase guidance</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">CLI executor</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- TDD -->
			<div class="example-card">
				<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">TDD enforcement</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
							<code>examples/tdd/</code>
						</p>
					</div>
					<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/tree/main/examples/tdd"
						class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap">
						View source
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
					Enforced red → green → refactor cycle. The LLM can't skip from
					red to refactor — the workflow won't let it. Includes cheat detection:
					if the model tries to write production code before a failing test,
					the guard catches it. Dogfooded in CI with a mechanical driver script.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">workflow enforcement</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">cheat detection</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">CI dogfood</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Simple configs -->
			<div class="example-card">
				<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Starter configs</h2>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
							<code>examples/</code>
						</p>
					</div>
					<a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/tree/main/examples"
						class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap">
						View source
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
					Small, focused configs for specific patterns: <code>simple-proxy.yaml</code>
					(basic MCP passthrough), <code>governed-change.yaml</code> (approval gate),
					<code>import-and-discovery.yaml</code> (importing tools from MCP servers).
					Good starting points when you know the pattern you want.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">proxy</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">import</span>
					<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs rounded-full font-medium">discovery</span>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<footer class="py-12 px-6 bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-800">
	<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-8">
		<div>
			<p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">mcp-flowgate</p>
			<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Composable MCP control layer.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex gap-12">
			<div>
				<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Resources</p>
				<ul class="space-y-1">
					<li><a href="/introduction" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-sm">Docs</a></li>
					<li><a href="/examples" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-sm">Examples</a></li>
					<li><a href="/blog" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-sm">Blog</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div>
				<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm mb-2">Community</p>
				<ul class="space-y-1">
					<li><a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-sm">GitHub</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://github.com/matt-cochran/mcp-flowgate/issues" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 text-sm">Issues</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

</Landing>
